<%# Thin shim: `Searchable#new` (in `app/controllers/concerns/searchable.rb`)
does `format.html` with no block, which uses ActionView's implicit
render lookup — and Searchable is shared across multiple search
controllers. Rather than wire a `render_search_new_view` hook through
the concern now (that pattern lives in `ApplicationController::Indexes`
already; see `render_index_view`), render the Phlex view from here
until another search controller migrates and a shared hook is
worthwhile. %>
<%= render(Views::Controllers::SpeciesLists::Search::New.new(
             search: @search,
             controller: controller,
             local: @local
           )) %>
